Package: mlesurv
Type: Package
Title: Bias Correction in the Parametric Proportional Hazards Model
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alexander Begun
Maintainer: Alexander Begun <alexander.begun@gmx.de>
Description: Fits Parametric Proportional Hazards Model with Frailty. Possible baseline hazards: 
             Exponential, Weibull, Gompertz. 
             Possible frailty distributions: 
             gamma, inverse gaussian. 
             Calculates the Bias Correction for Maximum Likelihood Estimates.
             Expectations are calculated using the Monte Carlo integration.
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/AB5103/mlesurv
